ApplicationService
@Service("ApplicationServiceImpl")
@Transactional
public class ApplicationServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ApplicationService
This is the Implementation class. This class defines the application's boundary and its set of available operations from the perspective of interfacing client layers. It encapsulates the application's business logic, controlling transactions and co-ordinating responses in the implementation of its operations.
